<!--
HTML page displaying a header, footer, a filters box with dropdown, and results.

Layout: (based on 6-index.html)

Add Places section:
- Tag: section
- Classname: places
- Same level as the filters section, inside .container
- Contains a title:
  - Tag: h1
  - Text: Places
  - Align in the top left
  - Font size: 30px
- Contains multiple “Places” as listing (horizontal or vertical) described by:
  - Tag: article
  - Width: 390px
  - Padding and margin: 20px
  - Border: #FF5A5F 1px with radius 4px
  - Contains the place name:
    - Tag: h2
    - Font size: 30px
    - Center horizontally

Requirements:
- Use: header, footer, section, article, button, h1, h2, h3, h4, ul, li tags
- No inline style
- Do not use the img tag
- Do not use the style tag in the head tag
- All images must be stored in the images folder
- Must have 5 CSS files:
  - styles/4-common.css: for global style (i.e. body and .container styles)
  - styles/3-header.css: for the header style
  - styles/3-footer.css: for footer style
  - styles/6-filters.css: for the filters style
  - styles/7-places.css: for the places style
-->


